OL,4,Capproved
OL,6,FBristol's first liveable neighbourhood
OL,7,Fhas been given the go-ahead following
OL,8,Ftwo years of consultations.
OL,10,FThe controversial scheme aims to
OL,11,Freduce traffic and improve air quality
OL,12,Fin Barton Hill, St George and parts of
OL,13,FRedfield by putting road blocks in
OL,14,Fplace - prioritising cyclists and
OL,15,Fpedestrians.
OL,17,FAn initial pilot scheme will begin
OL,18,Flater in 2024, although a start date
OL,19,Fwon't be confirmed until after
OL,20,FBristol's election on 2 May.
