OL,6,FBristol City Council has said the
OL,7,Fscheme will be monitored by transport
OL,8,Fchiefs.
OL,10,FFollowing a council meeting on Friday
OL,11,F15 March, transport chief Cllr Don
OL,12,FAlexander said: "We're aiming to
OL,13,Fdeliver a safe, healthy, inclusive,
OL,14,Fand attractive environment where
OL,15,Feveryone can breathe clean air, have
OL,16,Faccess to better quality green spaces,
OL,17,Fand feel a part of their community.
