OL,6,F"To do this we need to change the
OL,7,Flayout of some local roads to make
OL,8,Fthem safer and to discourage drivers
OL,9,Fusing them as shortcuts.
OL,11,F"Elsewhere, this has been shown to
OL,12,Fboost active travel in neighbourhoods,
OL,13,Freducing traffic and congestion on the
OL,14,Froads, which brings with it all the
OL,15,Fhealth benefits of getting exercise
OL,16,Fand feeling a part of your community.
