OL,6,F"If the pilot scheme is deemed
OL,7,Fsuccessful, the trial measures would
OL,8,Fbe replaced with permanent
OL,9,Finfrastructure that would also include
OL,10,Fextra street lighting, new crossings
OL,11,Fwith traffic signals, sections of
OL,12,Fcycle track and street trees."
OL,14,FBristol City Council will begin by
OL,15,Finstalling 15 cycle hangars in 14
OL,16,Fstreets across the area, with the
OL,17,Ffirst four going in next week on
OL,18,FHolmes Street, Avonvale Road, Victoria
OL,19,FAvenue/Witchell Road and Diamond Road.
